nents"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Chips help people enter information, make selections, filter content, or trigger actions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"suggestion chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is a compact UI element used to present recommended or predictive options based on user input or context."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This version of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"suggestion chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" uses the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"text only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout which displays only text, offering a clean and minimalistic look."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Other layouts are available for this component like: "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"text + icon","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip"}}}